<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-07-10T12:47:43-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-07-10T12:47:43-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T12:47:43-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊新推出的 Echo Spot 在 Prime Day 已经有近半价折扣</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;床头柜上有一个 Amazon Echo Spot 智能音箱/闹钟，还有一杯热茶。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NVNyhOIazg4geU48dHvKJVVlemc=/0x43:1000x710/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73453396/61Eu2owyKEL._AC_SL1000_.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：亚马逊&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fn9hUn&quot;>;亚马逊的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/amazon-prime-day-deals-tech&quot; >;Prime Day&lt;/a>; 距离&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/25/24145258/amazon-prime-day-dates-july-2024-sale&quot;>;不到一周远&lt;/a>;，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24186583/amazon-prime-day-2024-best-tech-deals-sales&quot;>;早期优惠&lt;/a>;智能家居设备，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/All-new-Amazon-Echo-Spot-2024-release-Smart-alarm-clock-with-vibrant-sound-Alexa-Black/dp /B0BFC7WQ6R?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>; 已开始销售多年前的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /7/8/24194272/amazon-echo-spot-alexa-smart-speaker&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Echo Spot&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;&lt;strong>; &lt;/strong>;现价 44.99 美元（立减 35 美元），Prime 专享成员。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;mkX9Fk&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;为什么智能闹钟不可信&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22727055/alexa-google-smart-speaker-alarm-clocks -backup-battery&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊全新的人工智能 Alexa 每月费用可能高达 10 美元&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/21/24183013 /amazon-alexa-ai-subscription&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;YHrJaV&quot;>;点赞 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2017/9/28/16378472/amazons-echo-spot-camera-in-your-bedroom&quot;>;前身&lt;/a>;，新的 Spot 是智能音箱和闹钟的组合，但它放弃了没人喜欢的摄像头放在他们的卧室里。它现在还借用了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23742395/amazon-echo-pop-smart-speaker-review&quot;>;Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 的设计，亚马逊声称应该提供这种设计它的音质更好。作为一款 Echo 扬声器，它当然支持 Alexa 语音命令来设置早晨的闹钟、调出天气预报或向您朗读新闻更新。如果你的卧室里有麦克风仍然感觉令人毛骨悚然，Spot 的顶部有一个专门的按钮可以打开它......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /7/10/24195655/amazon-echo-spot-smart-alarm-clock-prime-day-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195655/amazon-echo-spot-smart-alarm-clock-prime-day-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195655/amazon-echo-spot-smart-alarm-clock-prime-day-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T12:10:56-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T12:10:56-04:00</updated><title>您可以在此处预订三星 Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Galaxy Z Flip 6</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 智能手机的上手照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/r4QyXE_fR1irngdl0NN9BB3HpA0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73453331/DSCF8101.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;4gNhxR&quot;>;除了三款新的可穿戴设备（&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24194938 /samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price-unpacked-2024&quot;>;Galaxy Ring&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra- 7-hands-on-features-price&quot;>;Galaxy Watch 7 和 Watch Ultra&lt;/a>;）和一对新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds -3-pro-hands-on-preview-features&quot;>;Galaxy Buds 3 Pro&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy- unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;>;三星已在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 上解压详细信息&lt;/a>; 7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price&quot;>;两款最新的可折叠智能手机&lt;/a>;：Galaxy Z Fold 6（1,899.99 美元）和 Galaxy Z Flip 6（1,099.99 美元） 。两者都比前代产品带来了最小的改进，但起价却比以前的版本高出 100 美元。预订即日开始，设备将于 7 月 24 日开始发货。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;yG5WE6&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 有较小的更新和更高的价格&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何预订三星 Galaxy Watch 7、Galaxy Watch Ultra 和 Galaxy Ring&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price- availability-release-date&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星 Galaxy Unpacked：2024 年 7 月活动中宣布的所有内容&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/ samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;2lfiub&quot; >;Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Z Flip 6 最值得注意的是添加了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/24/23928867/qualcomm-snapdragon-8-gen-3-on-device -ai-meta-llama-2&quot;>;Snapdragon 8 Gen 3&lt;/a>;，这是高通最新的旗舰芯片组。它有一个专用的神经处理单元，用于处理不断增长的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/17/24040372/samsung-galaxy-s24-plus-price-release-date-specs -features-ai-artificial-intelligence&quot;>;Galaxy AI&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24176860/google-gemini-explained-ai-assistant&quot;>;Google Gemini&lt;/a >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23693781/google-android-14-features-update-io&quot;>;Android 14&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112896/galaxy-ai-cometh&quot;>;一个 UI 6&lt;/a>;。三星以更扁平的方式改进了其外观设计...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195208/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip -6-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195208/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195208/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T11:50:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T11:50:09-04:00</updated><title> Meta 现在可以让小孩子在 VR 中聊天——但前提是得到父母的批准</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Meta 徽标的图像，背景为红色和蓝色。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Y9p5A-Qabx4RO1Cp5Ilhye8_ItA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73453253/STK043_VRG_Illo_N_Barclay_1_Meta .0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Nick Barclay / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;BLvcf5&quot;>;Meta 现在可以让孩子们在虚拟现实中与其他用户互动，但前提是他们得到家长的批准。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta.com%2Fblog%2Fquest%2Fparent-approved-contacts-for- preteens%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F10%2F24195692%2Fmeta-quest-approved-contacts-parental-controls&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener “ target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;即将发生的变化&lt;/a>;将让家长单独批准他们 10 到 12 岁的孩子可以在 Quest 上打电话、聊天和加入 VR 体验的每个用户。此前，Meta 不允许该年龄段的孩子使用聊天、打电话或邀请他人玩游戏。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eKuOFI&quot;>;去年，Meta &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2023/6/16/23763812/meta-quest-headset-lower-age-10-years-old&quot;>;将可以使用 Quest 耳机的儿童的最低年龄从 13 岁降低到10岁。这个年龄段的孩子必须获得父母的批准才能为耳机创建元帐户，他们的父母可以控制该帐户。默认情况下，Meta 不会向这些帐户展示广告，只会推荐适合他们年龄的游戏和应用。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;我...&lt;/cite>;&lt; /figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195692/meta-quest-approved-contacts-parental-controls&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195692/meta-quest-approved-contacts-parental-controls" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195692/meta-quest-approved-contacts-parental-controls</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T11:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T11:00:00-04:00</updated><title>第一支全四肢瘫痪的电子竞技队创造了公平的竞争环境</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;四神中的理查德·雅各布斯和塞尔吉奥·阿塞维多&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/byh1xfCXIbeSwr7jCL_1cvtotX0=/76x0:904x552/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73453079/richard_jacobs_left_sergio_acevedo_right_.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 HBO 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;导演 Jess Jacklin 与 The Verge 谈论她继第一部之后的新纪录片 -四肢瘫痪的电子竞技队。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195198/quad-gods-documentary-jess-jacklin-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195198/quad-gods-documentary-jess-jacklin-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195198/quad-gods-documentary-jess-jacklin-interview</id><author><name>奥德白</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:35:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:35:02-04:00</updated><title>诉讼称现代经销商被迫推销“假”电动汽车销售</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;现代经销店&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-d_KzeXYCLmcb__dQ2F1O6y8GiI=/107x0:1253x764/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/73453039/2020_11_05.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Napleton Aurora Imports&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;