您必须等到 7 月 24 日才能正式上市，但所有可穿戴设备现在都可以在美国预订。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;juFBrU&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星 Galaxy Unpacked：夏季产品活动的所有新闻&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung- Galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星 Galaxy Watch 6 系列评测：精致，但并非革命性&quot;,&quot;url&quot;: &quot;https://www.theverge.com/23818557/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-review-bezels-smartwatch-wearables&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= &quot;geO0A2&quot;>;新款可穿戴设备面向广泛的受众，从休闲用户到户外运动员。三星 Galaxy Ring 是一款时尚的可穿戴设备，更像是一款谨慎的健康追踪器，而 Galaxy Watch 7 是一款智能手表，功能更强大&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195618 /the-galaxy-watch-ultra-get-fda-cleared-sleep-apnea-detection&quot;>;新的睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能&lt;/a>;。但它的功能并不像三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 那样丰富，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung -galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:23:37-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:23:37-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy 拆封：2024 年 7 月活动中宣布的所有内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色、蓝色和水绿色背景上的三星徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/j30lXEiclgq_A3r3_h4CIMAulZo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452722/acastro_STK075_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;三星推出了 Galaxy Ring、Galaxy Watch Ultra、新款 Z Fold 和 Z Flip 手机等。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>宋茜</name><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>最高法院 NetChoice 裁决的后果</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;最高法院大楼的照片插图，带有像素化的红白条纹。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-_j8bu4miMeay7jIXHchVU4QLYw=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452898/STK463_SCOTUS_D.0.jpg&quot;/ >; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |照片来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;以下是 SCOTUS 的决定对从儿童在线安全法到 TikTok“禁令”等各个方面可能意味着的含义。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>索尼新款 ZV-E10 II 相机旨在让视频博主远离 1,000 美元的手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色的索尼 ZV-E10 II，坐在桌子上，镜头已拆卸。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RzXhtCLNqP3vNHyi2owvJdAN2vk=/0x0:7726x5151/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452911/BFARSACE_ZVE10II_1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;ZV-E10 II 看起来非常像其 2021 年的前身。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7Gv7iG&quot;>;涓滴经济可能很垃圾，但索尼对于相机中的技术，仍然是坚定的信徒。新款 ZV-E10 II 延续了索尼的趋势，即从昂贵的相机到更实惠的型号进行小规模的迭代改变。只是它永远不会没有一些权衡。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;4LKvq5&quot;>;ZV-E10 II 是 APS-C 无反光镜系统相机的后续产品 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22702421/sony-alpha-zv-e10-review-vlogging-camera-test-price-specs&quot;>;2021 年的 ZV-E10&lt;/a>;，现在配备更大的电池、26 兆像素背照式传感器，并改进了 4K 视频。它还会&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1838825-REG%2Fsony_zv_e10_ii_mirrorless_camera。 html&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F10%2F24194506%2Fsony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot; rel= “赞助的 nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;主体费用为 999 美元&lt;/a>; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A% 2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1839377-REG%2Fsony_zv_e10_ii_mirrorless_camera.html&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F10%2F24194506% 2F索尼- alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;捆绑包售价 1,099 美元&lt;/a>; 搭配索尼新款 PZ 16-50mm f/3.5-5.6 OSS II 镜头于 8 月初推出 - 价格大约是旗舰手机的价格，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899983/iphone-15-pro-max-camera-apple-full-框架&quot;>;iPhone 15 Pro Max&lt;/a>;。但是，当然，即使是最好的 iPhone 相机也有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii -vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 有较小的更新和更高的价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 智能手机的上手照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I66riB7OyE8CUtS7R-uBM9xNMu4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452748/DSCF8089.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;炎热的可折叠夏天正如火如荼地进行，你们大家。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;opCbaW&quot;>;如果您还有任何剩余的希望，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/ 3/24191966/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-spec-leak&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188017/ samsung-galaxy-z-flip-fold-6-leak-renders-colors-unpacked&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>;，三星的可折叠手机今年将进行重大更新，那么我不想成为坏消息的传播者。它们更耐用一点，更轻一点，并且有一些微小的升级。即便如此，这两款机型&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cmDKOyRtZR8&quot;>;都获得了一定程度的提升&lt;/a>;：价格上涨，Galaxy Z Fold 6 现在起价为 1,899 美元，Z Flip 起价为6 件售价 1,099 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WjhfvK&quot;>;两款手机均采用专门为三星调校的 Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 芯片组，与 S24 系列一样，它们都包含七年的操作系统和安全更新支持。由于铰链设计和材料的改进，它们都更加坚固，并声称具有更好的抗跌落能力。内部柔性玻璃也更耐用，而且...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z- Fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry></feed>